{"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"weekOfYear","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Int"},{"text":" { ","kind":"text"},{"text":"get","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" }"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The first week of the year is week 1.  This is the week that contains","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the first Thursday of the year.  Equivalently, this is the first week"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"that has more than 4 of its days falling within the calendar year.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The value 0 is never returned by this function.  Days contained","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"within a year but occurring before the first ISO 8601 week of that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"year are considered as being contained in the last week of the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"previous year.  Similarly, the final days of a calendar year may be"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"considered as being part of the first ISO 8601 week of the next year","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"if 4 or more days of that week are contained within the new year.","type":"text"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"abstract":[{"text":"Returns the ISO 8601 week number for the week containing ","type":"text"},{"code":"datetime","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"The ISO 8601 week number is the same for every day of the week (from","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Moday through Sunday).  That can produce some unusual results"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"(described below).","type":"text"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/glib\/datetimeprotocol\/weekofyear"]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/DateTimeProtocol\/weekOfYear","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib","doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/DateTimeProtocol"]]},"metadata":{"title":"weekOfYear","symbolKind":"property","modules":[{"name":"GLib"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"weekOfYear","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"extendedModule":"GLib","roleHeading":"Instance Property","role":"symbol","externalID":"s:4GLib16DateTimeProtocolPAAE10weekOfYearSivp"},"references":{"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib","title":"GLib","kind":"symbol","role":"collection","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/glib","abstract":[]},"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib/DateTimeProtocol":{"url":"\/documentation\/glib\/datetimeprotocol","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"protocol","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"DateTimeProtocol","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/DateTimeProtocol","abstract":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GDateTime"},{"text":" is a structure that combines a Gregorian date and time","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"into a single structure.","type":"text"}],"title":"DateTimeProtocol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"DateTimeProtocol"}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic"},"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib/DateTimeProtocol/weekOfYear":{"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"weekOfYear","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int"}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/glib\/datetimeprotocol\/weekofyear","abstract":[{"text":"Returns the ISO 8601 week number for the week containing ","type":"text"},{"code":"datetime","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The ISO 8601 week number is the same for every day of the week (from","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Moday through Sunday).  That can produce some unusual results"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"(described below).","type":"text"}],"title":"weekOfYear","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/DateTimeProtocol\/weekOfYear"}}}